{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JgbMZw5bYepUxfvUm3sxmg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Comprehensive Analysis:\n\n1. Directory Structure:\n   - Maven project structure\n   - Main Java source code: `/src/main/java`\n   - Test source code: `/src/test/java`\n   - Resources: `/src/main/resources`\n   - Multiple runtime configurations (Liberty, Glassfish, Payara, Tomee, Wildfly)\n\n2. Build System:\n   - Apache Maven (pom.xml)\n   - Version: 10.0.0.18-SNAPSHOT\n   - GroupId: org.woehlke.jakartaee\n   - ArtifactId: petclinic-jakartaee\n\n3. Java Source Files:\n   - Packages:\n     - `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic`\n     - Subpackages: \n       - `owner`\n       - `pet`\n       - `pettype`\n       - `specialty`\n       - `vet`\n       - `visit`\n       - `application`\n\n4. Configuration Files:\n   - Liberty: \n     - `/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml`\n     - `/src/main/liberty/config/userRegistry.xml`\n   - Persistence: \n     - Multiple `persistence.xml` for different runtimes\n   - Web: \n     - Multiple `web.xml` for different servers\n     - `faces-config.xml`\n     - `beans.xml`\n\n5. Dockerfile Analysis:\n   - Base image: maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n   - Uses PostgreSQL database\n   - Includes Playwright for testing\n   - Creates database for the application\n   - Runs application using Maven Liberty plugin\n\n6. Jakarta EE Specifics:\n   - Jakarta EE API dependencies\n   - Microprofile support\n   - JAX-RS (RESTful services)\n   - JPA (Persistence)\n   - CDI (Contexts and Dependency Injection)\n   - Faces (JSF)\n   - Arquillian for testing\n\n7. Testing:\n   - JUnit Jupiter (JUnit 5)\n   - Arquillian for integration testing\n   - UI and Unit tests\n   - Selenium/Playwright for UI testing\n\n8. Frameworks and Libraries:\n   - PrimeFaces (UI Component Library)\n   - RESTEasy\n   - Yasson (JSON Processing)\n   - Lombok\n   - Log4j\n   - SLF4J\n\nKey Files I recommend reviewing:\n1. `/pom.xml`\n2. `/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml`\n3. `/src/main/runtimes/liberty/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n4. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java`\n\nWould you like me to read and provide details about any specific files or go deeper into any particular aspect of the project?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"7c582831-3f73-4305-9228-2d7578839a4b"}
