{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MDHHLZc1tQtomepzpTD3sQ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\">\n     2→    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>\n     3→\n     4→    <groupId>org.woehlke.jakartaee</groupId>\n     5→    <artifactId>petclinic-jakartaee</artifactId>\n     6→    <packaging>war</packaging>\n     7→    <version>10.0.0.18-SNAPSHOT</version>\n     8→\n     9→    <name>Petclinic Jakarta EE 10</name>\n    10→    <description>\n    11→        Petclinic Jakarta EE - a Jakarta EE 10 Version of Spring Petclinic demo application using PrimeFaces JSF.\n    12→    </description>\n    13→    <url>https://java.woehlke.org/jakartaee/petclinic-jakartaee</url>\n    14→\n    15→    <organization>\n    16→        <name>Jakarta-EE-Petclinic</name>\n    17→        <url>https://github.com/Jakarta-EE-Petclinic</url>\n    18→    </organization>\n    19→    <inceptionYear>2019</inceptionYear>\n    20→\n    21→    <developers>\n    22→        <developer>\n    23→            <id>thomaswoehlke</id>\n    24→            <name>Thomas Woehlke</name>\n    25→            <email>thomas.woehlke@gmail.com</email>\n    26→            <url>https://github.com/thomaswoehlke</url>\n    27→            <timezone>Europe/Paris</timezone>\n    28→        </developer>\n    29→    </developers>\n    30→\n    31→    <scm>\n    32→        <connection>scm:git:git@github.com:Jakarta-EE-Petclinic/petclinic-jakartaee.git</connection>\n    33→        <developerConnection>scm:git:git@github.com:Jakarta-EE-Petclinic/petclinic-jakartaee.git</developerConnection>\n    34→        <url>https://github.com/Jakarta-EE-Petclinic/petclinic-jakartaee/tree/${project.scm.tag}</url>\n    35→        <tag>HEAD</tag>\n    36→    </scm>\n    37→\n    38→    <issueManagement>\n