{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_018DtVevZJV7iQdpgxiKdQTP","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully read all the requested files. Here's a comprehensive summary of the complete file contents:\n\n---\n\n# Complete File Contents - Pet Clinic Jakarta EE Application\n\n## Entity Models\n\n### 1. Owner.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, firstName, lastName, address, houseNumber, addressInfo, city, zipCode, phoneNumber, email, searchindex\n- Table: `owner` with unique constraints on uuid, email, and combination of names/city/phone\n- Named queries: `Owner.getAll`, `Owner.search`\n- Entity listener: `OwnerListener`\n- Validation: @NotEmpty on most fields, @Email, @Pattern for phone/zipCode\n- Uses Lombok annotations and extends EntityBaseObject\n\n### 2. Pet.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, birthDate, type (ManyToOne PetType), owner (ManyToOne Owner), searchindex\n- Table: `owner_pet` with unique constraint on name/birthDate/petType/owner\n- Named queries: `Pet.getAll`, `Pet.getPetsAsList`\n- Entity listener: `PetListener`\n- Eager fetching for relationships\n\n### 3. PetType.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, searchindex\n- Table: `owner_pet_pettype` with unique constraint on name\n- Named queries: `PetType.getAll`, `PetType.findByName`, `PetType.search`\n- Static factory methods: `newEntity()`\n\n### 4. Specialty.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, searchindex\n- Table: `specialty` with unique constraint on name\n- Named queries: `Specialty.getAll`, `Specialty.findSpecialtyByName`, `Specialty.search`\n- JAXB annotations for XML support\n\n### 5. Vet.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, firstName, lastName, specialties (ManyToMany Set<Specialty>)\n- Table: `vet` with join table `vet_specialties`\n- Named queries: `Vet.getAll`, `Vet.search`\n- Methods: getSpecialtiesAsString(), addSpecialty(), removeSpecialties()\n\n### 6. Visit.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java`\n\nComplete entity with:\n- Fields: id, uuid, date, description, pet (ManyToOne Pet), searchindex\n- Table: `owner_pet_visit` with unique constraint on date/description/pet\n- Named queries: `Visit.getAll`, `Visit.getVisits`\n\n## REST Endpoints\n\nAll endpoints follow the same pattern with methods for list and single entity retrieval in both JSON and XML formats:\n\n### 7-12. Endpoint Classes\n- **OwnerEndpoint.java**: `/rest/owner/*` endpoints\n- **PetEndpoint.java**: `/rest/pet/*` endpoints\n- **PetTypeEndpoint.java**: `/rest/petType/*` endpoints\n- **SpecialtyEndpoint.java**: `/rest/specialty/*` endpoints\n- **VetEndpoint.java**: `/rest/vet/*` endpoints\n- **VisitEndpoint.java**: `/rest/visit/*` endpoints\n\nAll are @Stateless EJBs with paths: `/list`, `/{id}`, `/list+json`, `/{id}+json`, `/list+xml`, `/{id}+xml`\n\n## DTO Classes\n\n### 13-30. DTO and Utility Classes\nEach domain has three classes:\n- **Dto**: Individual entity DTO with @JsonbProperty and @XmlRootElement\n- **ListDto**: Collection wrapper with List<Dto>\n- **EndpointUtil**: Factory methods for converting entities to DTOs and serializing to JSON/XML\n\nExamples include:\n- OwnerDto with embedded PetListDto\n- PetDto with embedded VisitListDto and PetTypeDto\n- VetDto with embedded SpecialtyListDto\n- Date fields use @JsonbDateFormat(\"yyyy-MM-dd\")\n\n## Data Access Layer\n\n### 31-36. Owner DAO and Services\n- **OwnerDao**: Interface extending CrudDao and SearchableEntity\n- **OwnerDaoImpl**: JPA implementation with @PersistenceContext\n- **OwnerService**: Interface with addNewVisit(), getPetsAsList()\n- **OwnerServiceImpl**: Business logic implementation\n- **OwnerViewService**: Facade service interface\n- **OwnerViewServiceImpl**: Facade implementation coordinating multiple DAOs\n\nAll similar DAO/Service patterns exist for Pet, PetType, Specialty, Vet, and Visit entities.\n\n## Application Configuration\n\n### 37. PetclinicApplication.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java`\n\n```java\n@ApplicationScoped\n@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")\npublic class PetclinicApplication extends Application\n```\n\n## Framework Base Classes\n\n### 38-42. Framework Interfaces\n- **EntityBase**: Base interface with getId(), getUuid(), getTableName(), getPrimaryKey()\n- **EntityBaseObject**: Abstract base class implementing EntityBase\n- **CrudDao**: Generic DAO interface with getAll(), findById(), addNew(), update(), delete()\n- **CrudService**: Generic service interface mirroring DAO methods\n- **SearchableService**: Interface for search functionality\n\n## Configuration Files\n\n### persistence.xml (Wildfly example)\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/runtimes/wildfly/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n\n```xml\n<persistence-unit name=\"petclinicPersistenceUnit\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n    <jta-data-source>java:jboss/datasources/PostgreSQLDS</jta-data-source>\n    <!-- Lists all entity classes -->\n    <properties>\n        <property name=\"jakarta.persistence.schema-generation.database.action\" value=\"drop-and-create\"/>\n        <property name=\"javax.persistence.sql-load-script-source\" value=\"META-INF/sql/data.sql\"/>\n        <property name=\"hibernate.dialect\" value=\"org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect\"/>\n    </properties>\n</persistence-unit>\n```\n\n### beans.xml\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml`\n\n```xml\n<beans xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\" version=\"4.0\" bean-discovery-mode=\"annotated\">\n```\n\n### data.sql\n**Path:** Contains complete PostgreSQL database dump with sample data:\n- 2 Owners (Thomas Wöhlke, Justus Jonas)\n- 12 PetTypes (Dog, Cat, Mouse, Hamster, Rabbit, Fish, Pony, Guinea pig, Pigeon, Snake, Spider, Donkey)\n- 5 Pets (Roger, Jerry, Tom, Python, Tarantula)\n- 7 Visits (various routine visits)\n- 7 Specialties (Cardiologist, Radiologist, Rescue Doctor, Surgeon, Neurosurgeon, Anesthetist, Shaman)\n- 2 Vets (Marie Curie, Walther von der Vogelweide) with specialty associations\n\n## Architecture Summary\n\nThis is a **Jakarta EE Pet Clinic application** with:\n- **JPA entities** with full validation\n- **RESTful web services** (JAX-RS) supporting JSON and XML\n- **EJB services** for business logic\n- **CDI** for dependency injection\n- **PostgreSQL** database\n- **Multi-runtime support** (Wildfly, Payara, GlassFish, TomEE, Liberty)\n- **Full CRUD operations** via REST API\n- **Search functionality** with search index fields\n- **Entity listeners** for lifecycle callbacks\n- **DTO pattern** for API responses\n- **Lombok** for reducing boilerplate code\n\nThe application is completely self-contained with all entities, services, endpoints, and configuration files properly structured following Jakarta EE best practices."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"f98c47c9-5e15-4f25-9a4f-c0a543b8777c"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01QJm37fxdeP86g51Jtp59kS","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the requested files. Let me compile the complete response with all file contents.\n\n---\n\n## Complete File Contents\n\nI have successfully read all requested files. Here are the complete contents:\n\n### 1. PetDao.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDao.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport jakarta.validation.constraints.NotNull;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.CrudDao;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n/**\n * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n * User: tw\n * Date: 06.01.14\n * Time: 20:34\n * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n */\npublic interface PetDao extends CrudDao<Pet> {\n    long serialVersionUID = -7894365380280920804L;\n\n    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(@NotNull Owner owner);\n\n    List<Visit> getVisits(@NotNull Pet pet);\n\n}\n```\n\n### 2. PetDaoImpl.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport jakarta.persistence.EntityManager;\nimport jakarta.persistence.PersistenceContext;\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n\nimport jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\nimport jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\nimport jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\nimport jakarta.persistence.TypedQuery;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n/**\n * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n * User: tw\n * Date: 06.01.14\n * Time: 20:34\n * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n */\n@Log\n@Stateless\npublic class PetDaoImpl implements PetDao, Serializable {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -9149391932558758266L;\n\n    @PersistenceContext(unitName = PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME)\n    private EntityManager entityManager;\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner) {\n        TypedQuery<Pet> q = entityManager.createNamedQuery(\"Pet.getPetsAsList\", Pet.class);\n        q.setParameter(\"owner\",owner);\n        return q.getResultList();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Visit> getVisits(Pet pet) {\n        TypedQuery<Visit> q = entityManager.createNamedQuery( \"Visit.getVisits\", Visit.class);\n        q.setParameter(\"pet\",pet);\n        return q.getResultList();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet addNew(Pet pet) {\n        pet.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        //pet.updateSearchindex(); TODO\n        log.info(\"transient New Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        entityManager.persist(pet);\n        log.info(\"persistent New Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return pet;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getAll() {\n        TypedQuery<Pet> q = entityManager.createNamedQuery(\"Pet.getAll\", Pet.class);\n        return q.getResultList();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet findById(long petId) {\n        return entityManager.find(Pet.class, petId);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet update(Pet pet) {\n        //pet.updateSearchindex(); TODO\n        log.info(\"update Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return entityManager.merge(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        Pet p = this.findById(id);\n        log.info(\"delete Pet: \" + p.toString());\n        entityManager.remove(p);\n    }\n\n    @PostConstruct\n    public void postConstruct() {\n        log.info(\"postConstruct: \"+PetDaoImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    }\n\n    @PreDestroy\n    public void preDestroy() {\n        log.info(\"preDestroy: \"+PetDaoImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    }\n\n}\n```\n\n### 3. PetService.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetService.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport jakarta.validation.constraints.NotNull;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.CrudService;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n\n/**\n *\n */\npublic interface PetService extends CrudService<Pet>, Serializable {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = 7113444329343577727L;\n\n    List<Visit> getVisits(@NotNull Pet pet);\n\n    List<Pet> getAllPetsOfAnOwner(@NotNull Owner entity);\n\n}\n```\n\n### 4. PetServiceImpl.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetServiceImpl.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport jakarta.ejb.EJB;\nimport jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n\nimport jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\nimport jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n\n/**\n *\n */\n@Log\n@Stateless\npublic class PetServiceImpl implements PetService, Serializable  {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -2093524918552358722L;\n\n    @EJB\n    private PetDao petDao;\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet addNew(Pet pet) {\n        log.info(\"addNew Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return this.petDao.addNew(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getAll() {\n        return this.petDao.getAll();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet findById(long petId) {\n        return this.petDao.findById(petId);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet update(Pet pet) {\n        log.info(\"update Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return this.petDao.update(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete Pet: \" + id);\n        this.petDao.delete(id);\n    }\n\n\n    @PostConstruct\n    public void postConstruct() {\n        log.info(\"postConstruct: \"+PetServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    }\n\n    @PreDestroy\n    public void preDestroy() {\n        log.info(\"preDestroy: \"+PetServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Visit> getVisits(Pet pet) {\n        return this.petDao.getVisits(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getAllPetsOfAnOwner(Owner owner) {\n        return this.petDao.getPetsAsList(owner);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 5. PetTypeDao.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDao.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.CrudDao;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.SearchableEntity;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\n/**\n * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n * User: Fert\n * Date: 06.01.14\n * Time: 11:51\n * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n */\npublic interface PetTypeDao extends CrudDao<PetType>, SearchableEntity<PetType> {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = -8106442452154966621L;\n\n    PetType findByName(String name);\n}\n```\n\n### 6. PetTypeDaoImpl.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java`\n\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport jakarta.ejb.PostActivate;\nimport jakarta.ejb.PrePassivate;\nimport jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\nimport jakarta.persistence.EntityManager;\nimport jakarta.persistence.PersistenceContext;\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\nimport jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\nimport jakarta.persistence.TypedQuery;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n/**\n * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n * User: Fert\n * Date: 06.01.14\n * Time: 11:51\n * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n */\n@Log\n@Stateless\npublic class PetTypeDaoImpl implements PetTypeDao, Serializable {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -7332614951852278897L;\n\n    @PersistenceContext(unitName = PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME)\n    private EntityManager entityManager;\n\n    @Override\n    public List<PetType> getAll() {\n        TypedQuery<PetType> q = entityManager.createNamedQuery(\"PetType.getAll\", PetType.class);\n        return q.getResultList();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        PetType petType = entityManager.find(PetType.class, id);\n        log.info(\"delete PetType: \" + petType.toString());\n        entityManager.remove(petType);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public PetType addNew(PetType petType) {\n        log.info(\"addNew PetType: \" + petType.toString());\n        petType.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        if(petType.getId() !=