 }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: For each file, you MUST use the Read tool to read the file FIRST, and ONLY THEN use the Write tool. Use absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":762,"cache_read_input_tokens":78709,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":762,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":16547},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"0159b1e0-5f5d-41da-88ef-b6476097165e"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01QbAbq6nn29edV9L6utubGC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01HzFHo4sYnJQJd6GigFokiD","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate DTO and utility classes","prompt":"Migrate the Jakarta EE DTO and EndpointUtil classes to Spring Boot. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nFor each file, READ it first, then WRITE the Spring Boot version.\n\nKey changes for DTOs:\n- Remove JAXB annotations (@XmlRootElement, @XmlElement, @XmlAttribute, @XmlAccessorType)\n- Remove JSON-B annotations (@JsonbProperty, @JsonbDateFormat)\n- Add Jackson annotations (@JsonProperty, @JsonFormat)\n- Keep Lombok annotations\n- Remove Serializable (optional but not needed)\n\nKey changes for EndpointUtil:\n- Replace @Stateless with @Component\n- Remove JAXB/JSON-B serialization methods (dtoJsonFactory, dtoXmlFactory) since Spring handles serialization\n- Keep dtoFactory and dtoListFactory methods\n\n### 1. OwnerDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java\nWrite the updated version, converting JAXB/JSON-B to Jackson. Keep all fields (id, uuid, firstName, lastName, address, houseNumber, addressInfo, city, zipCode, phoneNumber, email). It also has a petList field (List of PetDto or similar).\n\n### 2. OwnerListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java\nWrite updated version.\n\n### 3. OwnerEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated version. Change @Stateless to @Component. Keep dtoFactory and dtoListFactory. Remove JAXB/JSON-B serialization methods.\n\n### 4. PetDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 5. PetListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 6. PetEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 7. PetTypeDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 8. PetTypeListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 9. PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 10. SpecialtyDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 11. SpecialtyListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 12. SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 13. VetDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 14. VetListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 15. Check for VetEndpointUtil.java - use Glob to check if it exists\nIf it exists, read and write. If not, create it.\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java\n\nThe VetEndpointUtil should convert Vet entities to VetDto:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.api;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@Component\npublic class VetEndpointUtil {\n\n    public VetDto dtoFactory(Vet vet) {\n        VetDto dto = new VetDto();\n        dto.setId(vet.getId());\n        dto.setUuid(vet.getUuid());\n        dto.setFirstName(vet.getFirstName());\n        dto.setLastName(vet.getLastName());\n        List<SpecialtyDto> specialtyDtos = new ArrayList<>();\n        if (vet.getSpecialties() != null) {\n            for (Specialty s : vet.getSpecialties()) {\n                SpecialtyDto sdto = new SpecialtyDto();\n                sdto.setId(s.getId());\n                sdto.setUuid(s.getUuid());\n                sdto.setName(s.getName());\n                specialtyDtos.add(sdto);\n            }\n        }\n        SpecialtyListDto specialtyListDto = new SpecialtyListDto();\n        specialtyListDto.setSpecialties(specialtyDtos);\n        dto.setSpecialtyList(specialtyListDto);\n        return dto;\n    }\n\n    public VetListDto dtoListFactory(List<Vet> vets) {\n        List<VetDto> dtoList = new ArrayList<>();\n        for (Vet vet : vets) {\n            dtoList.add(dtoFactory(vet));\n        }\n        VetListDto listDto = new VetListDto();\n        listDto.setVets(dtoList);\n        return listDto;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 16. VisitDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 17. VisitListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 18. VisitEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\nIMPORTANT RULES for DTOs:\n- Remove ALL jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.* imports\n- Remove ALL jakarta.json.bind.annotation.* imports  \n- Replace @JsonbProperty(\"fieldName\") with @JsonProperty(\"fieldName\") from com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation\n- Replace @JsonbDateFormat(\"yyyy-MM-dd\") with @JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\") from com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation\n- Add @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL) to DTOs if appropriate\n- Keep all Lombok annotations (@Getter, @Setter, @ToString, @EqualsAndHashCode, @NoArgsConstructor, @AllArgsConstructor)\n- For list DTOs, make sure they have a default constructor and proper getter/setter\n\nIMPORTANT RULES for EndpointUtil:\n- Replace @Stateless with @Component (from org.springframework.stereotype)\n- Remove @EJB, use @Autowired if needed\n- Remove dtoJsonFactory() and dtoXmlFactory() methods (Spring handles serialization)\n- Keep dtoFactory() and dtoListFactory() methods\n- Look at the actual entity-to-DTO mapping logic and preserve it\n- If EndpointUtil references other EndpointUtil classes (e.g., OwnerEndpointUtil uses PetEndpointUtil), inject them via @Autowired constructor\n\nFor each file, you MUST use the Read tool to read the file FIRST, and ONLY THEN use the Write tool. Use absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":762,"cache_read_input_tokens":78709,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":762,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":16547},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"69920e8f-2ffb-4fc0-be34-4dad18496c00"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You need to migrate Jakarta EE entity classes to Spring Boot compatible versions. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nIMPORTANT: Spring Boot 3.x uses jakarta.persistence.* annotations, so JPA annotations remain the same. The key changes are:\n- Remove JSF-specific imports and annotations  \n- Remove EJB-specific annotations\n- Keep all jakarta.persistence.* annotations as-is\n- Remove JAXB annotations (@XmlRootElement etc) since we'll use Jackson\n- Keep Lombok annotations\n- Keep validation annotations\n\n## Files to modify:\n\n### 1. Owner.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java\n\nThen rewrite it keeping all JPA annotations (they use jakarta.persistence which is correct for Spring Boot 3), validation annotations, Lombok annotations. Remove any JAXB annotations. Keep the entity exactly the same but clean up any JSF-specific code. Keep the @NamedQueries.\n\n### 2. Pet.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java\nSame approach - keep JPA, remove JAXB.\n\n### 3. PetType.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java\n\n### 4. Specialty.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java\n\n### 5. Vet.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java\n\n### 6. Visit.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java\n\n### 7. EntityBase.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBase.java\nKeep as-is, this is just an interface.\n\n### 8. EntityBaseObject.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead and rewrite /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBaseObject.java\nKeep as-is, remove any JAXB annotations.\n\n### 9. SearchableEntity.java - READ FIRST then WRITE  \nRead /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/SearchableEntity.java\nKeep as-is.\n\n### 10. EntityListenerLogger.java - READ FIRST then WRITE\nRead /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/EntityListenerLogger.java\nKeep as-is.\n\n### 11-16. All Listener classes - READ FIRST then WRITE each one\nOwnerListener, PetListener, PetTypeListener, SpecialtyListener, VetListener, VisitListener\nThese use jakarta.persistence lifecycle annotations which work fine with Spring Boot 3. Read and keep as-is.\n\nFor each file, READ it first, then WRITE the updated version.\n\nKEY RULES:\n- jakarta.persistence.* imports stay exactly the same\n- jakarta.validation.* imports stay exactly the same  \n- Remove jakarta.xml.bind.* imports (JAXB)\n- Remove @XmlRootElement, @XmlElement, @XmlAttribute, @XmlAccessorType etc\n- Remove jakarta.json.bind.* imports (JSON-B)\n- Remove @JsonbProperty, @JsonbDateFormat etc - we'll use Jackson instead\n- Add @JsonProperty from com.fasterxml.jackson where appropriate\n- Add @JsonFormat for date fields\n- Keep all @Entity, @Table, @Column, @Id, @GeneratedValue, @SequenceGenerator, @NamedQueries, @NamedQuery, @ManyToOne, @ManyToMany, @JoinTable, @JoinColumn, @EntityListeners, @UniqueConstraint annotations\n- Keep all @NotNull, @NotEmpty, @NotBlank, @Email, @Pattern, @Digits annotations\n- Keep all Lombok annotations (@Getter, @Setter, @EqualsAndHashCode, @ToString, @Log, etc.)\n- Keep @Cacheable(false) if present\n- Remove @Exportable if present (that's a UI annotation)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01G6ydnJ4xAimZCYyLPaAuGU","session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"970c8370-3112-4788-a497-d4baa4f1d6ae"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Create Spring Data JPA repository interfaces to replace the Jakarta EE DAO pattern. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nCreate the following repository files. Each one replaces the old CrudDao interface and implementation.\n\n### 1. OwnerRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface OwnerRepository extends JpaRepository<Owner, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT o FROM Owner o ORDER BY o.lastName, o.firstName\")\n    List<Owner> findAllOrderByName();\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT o FROM Owner o WHERE o.searchindex LIKE :searchterm ORDER BY o.lastName, o.firstName\")\n    List<Owner> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\n### 2. PetRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface PetRepository extends JpaRepository<Pet, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT p FROM Pet p ORDER BY p.name\")\n    List<Pet> findAllOrderByName();\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT p FROM Pet p WHERE p.owner = :owner ORDER BY p.name\")\n    List<Pet> findByOwner(@Param(\"owner\") Owner owner);\n}\n```\n\n### 3. PetTypeRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface PetTypeRepository extends JpaRepository<PetType, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT pt FROM PetType pt ORDER BY pt.name\")\n    List<PetType> findAllOrderByName();\n\n    PetType findByName(String name);\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT pt FROM PetType pt WHERE pt.searchindex LIKE :searchterm ORDER BY pt.name\")\n    List<PetType> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\n### 4. SpecialtyRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface SpecialtyRepository extends JpaRepository<Specialty, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT s FROM Specialty s ORDER BY s.name\")\n    List<Specialty> findAllOrderByName();\n\n    Specialty findByName(String name);\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT s FROM Specialty s WHERE s.searchindex LIKE :searchterm ORDER BY s.name\")\n    List<Specialty> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\n### 5. VetRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface VetRepository extends JpaRepository<Vet, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT v FROM Vet v ORDER BY v.lastName, v.firstName\")\n    List<Vet> findAllOrderByName();\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT v FROM Vet v WHERE v.searchindex LIKE :searchterm ORDER BY v.lastName, v.firstName\")\n    List<Vet> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\n### 6. VisitRepository.java\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface VisitRepository extends JpaRepository<Visit, Long> {\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT v FROM Visit v ORDER BY v.date DESC\")\n    List<Visit> findAllOrderByDate();\n\n    @Query(\"SELECT v FROM Visit v WHERE v.pet = :pet ORDER BY v.date DESC\")\n    List<Visit> findByPet(@Param(\"pet\") Pet pet);\n}\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: Use the Write tool to create each file. Use the full absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JHaq3oYbBWMcLsutvsU8rn","session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"592186c5-f1a7-4e48-94d6-0ca79f7f293e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migrate the Jakarta EE service classes to Spring Boot. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nFor each file, READ it first, then WRITE the Spring Boot version.\n\nKey changes for all services:\n- Replace @Stateless with @Service\n- Replace @EJB with @Autowired  \n- Add @Transactional where needed\n- Replace @PostConstruct/@PreDestroy (keep if using jakarta.annotation - these work in Spring)\n- Remove Serializable interface (not needed in Spring)\n- Use the new Repository interfaces instead of DAO interfaces\n\n### 1. OwnerServiceImpl.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerServiceImpl.java\nThen WRITE the updated file:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetRepository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitRepository;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class OwnerServiceImpl implements OwnerService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -5765751616265629L;\n\n    private final OwnerRepository ownerRepository;\n    private final PetRepository petRepository;\n    private final VisitRepository visitRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public OwnerServiceImpl(OwnerRepository ownerRepository, PetRepository petRepository, VisitRepository visitRepository) {\n        this.ownerRepository = ownerRepository;\n        this.petRepository = petRepository;\n        this.visitRepository = visitRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Owner> getAll() {\n        return ownerRepository.findAllOrderByName();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner findById(long id) {\n        return ownerRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner addNew(Owner owner) {\n        owner.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Owner: \" + owner.toString());\n        return ownerRepository.save(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner update(Owner owner) {\n        log.info(\"update Owner: \" + owner.toString());\n        return ownerRepository.save(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete Owner: \" + id);\n        ownerRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Owner> search(String searchterm) {\n        return ownerRepository.search(\"%\" + searchterm + \"%\");\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void resetSearchIndex() {\n        // no-op\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit) {\n        visit.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNewVisit: \" + visit.toString());\n        return visitRepository.save(visit);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner) {\n        return petRepository.findByOwner(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public String getPetsAsString(Owner owner) {\n        List<Pet> pets = getPetsAsList(owner);\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n        for (Pet pet : pets) {\n            sb.append(pet.getName()).append(\" \");\n        }\n        return sb.toString().trim();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Also update OwnerService.java interface\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerService.java  \nRewrite removing EJB dependencies:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface OwnerService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = -3020781892498524067L;\n\n    List<Owner> getAll();\n    Owner findById(long id);\n    Owner addNew(Owner owner);\n    Owner update(Owner owner);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Owner> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit);\n    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner);\n    String getPetsAsString(Owner owner);\n}\n```\n\n### 3. PetServiceImpl.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetServiceImpl.java\nWrite updated:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitRepository;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class PetServiceImpl implements PetService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -2093524918552358722L;\n\n    private final PetRepository petRepository;\n    private final VisitRepository visitRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public PetServiceImpl(PetRepository petRepository, VisitRepository visitRepository) {\n        this.petRepository = petRepository;\n        this.visitRepository = visitRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet addNew(Pet pet) {\n        pet.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return petRepository.save(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getAll() {\n        return petRepository.findAllOrderByName();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet findById(long petId) {\n        return petRepository.findById(petId).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Pet update(Pet pet) {\n        log.info(\"update Pet: \" + pet.toString());\n        return petRepository.save(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete Pet: \" + id);\n        petRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Visit> getVisits(Pet pet) {\n        return visitRepository.findByPet(pet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getAllPetsOfAnOwner(Owner owner) {\n        return petRepository.findByOwner(owner);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. PetService.java interface\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface PetService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = 7113444329343577727L;\n\n    Pet addNew(Pet pet);\n    List<Pet> getAll();\n    Pet findById(long petId);\n    Pet update(Pet pet);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Visit> getVisits(Pet pet);\n    List<Pet> getAllPetsOfAnOwner(Owner entity);\n}\n```\n\n### 5. PetTypeServiceImpl.java\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class PetTypeServiceImpl implements PetTypeService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = -6242995649030237034L;\n\n    private final PetTypeRepository petTypeRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public PetTypeServiceImpl(PetTypeRepository petTypeRepository) {\n        this.petTypeRepository = petTypeRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<PetType> getAll() {\n        return petTypeRepository.findAllOrderByName();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete PetType: \" + id);\n        petTypeRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public PetType addNew(PetType petType) {\n        petType.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew PetType: \" + petType.toString());\n        return petTypeRepository.save(petType);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public PetType findById(long id) {\n        return petTypeRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public PetType update(PetType petType) {\n        log.info(\"update PetType: \" + petType.toString());\n        return petTypeRepository.save(petType);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<PetType> search(String searchterm) {\n        return petTypeRepository.search(\"%\" + searchterm + \"%\");\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void resetSearchIndex() {\n        // no-op\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public PetType findByName(String name) {\n        return petTypeRepository.findByName(name);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. PetTypeService.java interface\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface PetTypeService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = 6637453269836393L;\n\n    List<PetType> getAll();\n    void delete(long id);\n    PetType addNew(PetType petType);\n    PetType findById(long id);\n    PetType update(PetType petType);\n    List<PetType> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    PetType findByName(String name);\n}\n```\n\n### 7. SpecialtyServiceImpl.java\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class SpecialtyServiceImpl implements SpecialtyService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 6145428275502469961L;\n\n    private final SpecialtyRepository specialtyRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public SpecialtyServiceImpl(SpecialtyRepository specialtyRepository) {\n        this.specialtyRepository = specialtyRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Specialty> getAll() {\n        return specialtyRepository.findAllOrderByName();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Specialty findById(long id) {\n        return specialtyRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Specialty addNew(Specialty specialty) {\n        specialty.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Specialty: \" + specialty.toString());\n        return specialtyRepository.save(specialty);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Specialty update(Specialty specialty) {\n        log.info(\"update Specialty: \" + specialty.toString());\n        return specialtyRepository.save(specialty);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete Specialty: \" + id);\n        specialtyRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Specialty> search(String searchterm) {\n        return specialtyRepository.search(\"%\" + searchterm + \"%\");\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void resetSearchIndex() {\n        // no-op\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Specialty findSpecialtyByName(String name) {\n        return specialtyRepository.findByName(name);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 8. SpecialtyService.java interface\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface SpecialtyService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = -5259594533899166058L;\n\n    List<Specialty> getAll();\n    Specialty findById(long id);\n    Specialty addNew(Specialty specialty);\n    Specialty update(Specialty specialty);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Specialty> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    Specialty findSpecialtyByName(String name);\n}\n```\n\n### 9. VetServiceImpl.java\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class VetServiceImpl implements VetService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 2698313227542867286L;\n\n    private final VetRepository vetRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public VetServiceImpl(VetRepository vetRepository) {\n        this.vetRepository = vetRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Vet> getAll() {\n        return vetRepository.findAllOrderByName();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Vet findById(long id) {\n        return vetRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete Vet: \" + id);\n        vetRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Vet addNew(Vet vet) {\n        vet.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Vet: \" + vet.toString());\n        return vetRepository.save(vet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Vet update(Vet vet) {\n        log.info(\"update Vet: \" + vet.toString());\n        return vetRepository.save(vet);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Vet> search(String searchterm) {\n        return vetRepository.search(\"%\" + searchterm + \"%\");\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void resetSearchIndex() {\n        // no-op\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 10. VetService.java interface\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface VetService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = 6211608636423556157L;\n\n    List<Vet> getAll();\n    Vet findById(long id);\n    void delete(long id);\n    Vet addNew(Vet vet);\n    Vet update(Vet vet);\n    List<Vet> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n}\n```\n\n### 11. VisitServiceImpl.java\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class VisitServiceImpl implements VisitService {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 4560958540651968289L;\n\n    private final VisitRepository visitRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public VisitServiceImpl(VisitRepository visitRepository) {\n        this.visitRepository = visitRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Visit> getAll() {\n        return visitRepository.findAllOrderByDate();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Visit findById(long id) {\n        return visitRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Visit addNew(Visit visit) {\n        visit.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Visit: \" + visit.toString());\n        return visitRepository.save(visit);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Visit update(Visit visit) {\n        log.info(\"update Visit: \" + visit.toString());\n        return visitRepository.save(visit);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        log.info(\"delete: \" + id);\n        visitRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Visit> getAllVisitsOfAnPet(Pet pet) {\n        return visitRepository.findByPet(pet);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 12. VisitService.java interface\nRead then write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface VisitService {\n\n    long serialVersionUID = -207047254562666324L;\n\n    List<Visit> getAll();\n    Visit findById(long id);\n    Visit addNew(Visit visit);\n    Visit update(Visit visit);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Visit> getAllVisitsOfAnPet(Pet pet);\n}\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: For each file, you MUST use the Read tool to read the file FIRST, and ONLY THEN use the Write tool. Use absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01KQYtxmX9vcjZ7tUQvv7GSz","session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"0fbe585e-6ebb-47f5-b4e7-e70d9e312e42"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migrate the Jakarta EE JAX-RS endpoints to Spring Boot REST controllers. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nFor each file, READ it first, then WRITE the Spring Boot version.\n\nKey changes:\n- Replace @Path with @RestController + @RequestMapping\n- Replace @GET with @GetMapping\n- Replace @Produces with produces parameter in mapping\n- Replace @PathParam with @PathVariable\n- Replace @Stateless + @EJB with @Autowired\n- Return ResponseEntity or direct objects\n- Keep same URL paths under /rest prefix\n\n### 1. OwnerEndpoint.java → OwnerController.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java\nThen write OwnerEndpoint.java (keep same filename to avoid breaking references):\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api.OwnerDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api.OwnerEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api.OwnerListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db.OwnerService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/owner\")\npublic class OwnerEndpoint {\n\n    private final OwnerService ownerService;\n    private final OwnerEndpointUtil ownerEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public OwnerEndpoint(OwnerService ownerService, OwnerEndpointUtil ownerEndpointUtil) {\n        this.ownerService = ownerService;\n        this.ownerEndpointUtil = ownerEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<Owner> owners = ownerService.getAll();\n        OwnerListDto dto = ownerEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(owners);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        Owner owner = ownerService.findById(id);\n        if (owner == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        OwnerDto dto = ownerEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(owner);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<OwnerDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. PetEndpoint.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java\nThen write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/pet\")\npublic class PetEndpoint {\n\n    private final PetService petService;\n    private final PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public PetEndpoint(PetService petService, PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil) {\n        this.petService = petService;\n        this.petEndpointUtil = petEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<PetListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<Pet> pets = petService.getAll();\n        PetListDto dto = petEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(pets);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<PetDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        Pet pet = petService.findById(id);\n        if (pet == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        PetDto dto = petEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(pet);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. PetTypeEndpoint.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java\nThen write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/petType\")\npublic class PetTypeEndpoint {\n\n    private final PetTypeService petTypeService;\n    private final PetTypeEndpointUtil petTypeEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public PetTypeEndpoint(PetTypeService petTypeService, PetTypeEndpointUtil petTypeEndpointUtil) {\n        this.petTypeService = petTypeService;\n        this.petTypeEndpointUtil = petTypeEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<PetType> petTypes = petTypeService.getAll();\n        PetTypeListDto dto = petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypes);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        PetType petType = petTypeService.findById(id);\n        if (petType == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        PetTypeDto dto = petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petType);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<PetTypeDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. SpecialtyEndpoint.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java\nThen write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db.SpecialtyService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/specialty\")\npublic class SpecialtyEndpoint {\n\n    private final SpecialtyService specialtyService;\n    private final SpecialtyEndpointUtil specialtyEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public SpecialtyEndpoint(SpecialtyService specialtyService, SpecialtyEndpointUtil specialtyEndpointUtil) {\n        this.specialtyService = specialtyService;\n        this.specialtyEndpointUtil = specialtyEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<Specialty> specialties = specialtyService.getAll();\n        SpecialtyListDto dto = specialtyEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(specialties);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        Specialty specialty = specialtyService.findById(id);\n        if (specialty == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        SpecialtyDto dto = specialtyEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(specialty);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<SpecialtyDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 5. VetEndpoint.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java\nThen write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.api.VetDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.api.VetEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.api.VetListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db.VetService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/vet\")\npublic class VetEndpoint {\n\n    private final VetService vetService;\n    private final VetEndpointUtil vetEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public VetEndpoint(VetService vetService, VetEndpointUtil vetEndpointUtil) {\n        this.vetService = vetService;\n        this.vetEndpointUtil = vetEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<VetListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<Vet> vets = vetService.getAll();\n        VetListDto dto = vetEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(vets);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<VetDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        Vet vet = vetService.findById(id);\n        if (vet == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        VetDto dto = vetEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(vet);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VetListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VetDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VetListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VetDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. VisitEndpoint.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java\nThen write:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.http.MediaType;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.api.VisitDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.api.VisitEndpointUtil;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.api.VisitListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitService;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/rest/visit\")\npublic class VisitEndpoint {\n\n    private final VisitService visitService;\n    private final VisitEndpointUtil visitEndpointUtil;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public VisitEndpoint(VisitService visitService, VisitEndpointUtil visitEndpointUtil) {\n        this.visitService = visitService;\n        this.visitEndpointUtil = visitEndpointUtil;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/list\")\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitListDto> getList() {\n        log.info(\"getList\");\n        List<Visit> visits = visitService.getAll();\n        VisitListDto dto = visitEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(visits);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/{id}\")\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitDto> getEntity(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        log.info(\"getEntity: \" + id);\n        Visit visit = visitService.findById(id);\n        if (visit == null) {\n            return ResponseEntity.notFound().build();\n        }\n        VisitDto dto = visitEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(visit);\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(dto);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitListDto> getListAsJson() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+json\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitDto> getEntityAsJson(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/list+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitListDto> getListAsXml() {\n        return getList();\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(value = \"/{id}+xml\", produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_XML_VALUE)\n    public ResponseEntity<VisitDto> getEntityAsXml(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long id) {\n        return getEntity(id);\n    }\n}\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: For each file, you MUST use the Read tool to read the file FIRST, and ONLY THEN use the Write tool. Use absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Bqgb2WRS6z1BcjyAdtLxz9","session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"a2dffc69-73e5-4243-8249-e32da6711b3f"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migrate the Jakarta EE DTO and EndpointUtil classes to Spring Boot. The project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nFor each file, READ it first, then WRITE the Spring Boot version.\n\nKey changes for DTOs:\n- Remove JAXB annotations (@XmlRootElement, @XmlElement, @XmlAttribute, @XmlAccessorType)\n- Remove JSON-B annotations (@JsonbProperty, @JsonbDateFormat)\n- Add Jackson annotations (@JsonProperty, @JsonFormat)\n- Keep Lombok annotations\n- Remove Serializable (optional but not needed)\n\nKey changes for EndpointUtil:\n- Replace @Stateless with @Component\n- Remove JAXB/JSON-B serialization methods (dtoJsonFactory, dtoXmlFactory) since Spring handles serialization\n- Keep dtoFactory and dtoListFactory methods\n\n### 1. OwnerDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java\nWrite the updated version, converting JAXB/JSON-B to Jackson. Keep all fields (id, uuid, firstName, lastName, address, houseNumber, addressInfo, city, zipCode, phoneNumber, email). It also has a petList field (List of PetDto or similar).\n\n### 2. OwnerListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java\nWrite updated version.\n\n### 3. OwnerEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated version. Change @Stateless to @Component. Keep dtoFactory and dtoListFactory. Remove JAXB/JSON-B serialization methods.\n\n### 4. PetDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 5. PetListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 6. PetEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 7. PetTypeDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 8. PetTypeListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 9. PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 10. SpecialtyDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 11. SpecialtyListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 12. SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 13. VetDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 14. VetListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 15. Check for VetEndpointUtil.java - use Glob to check if it exists\nIf it exists, read and write. If not, create it.\nWrite to: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java\n\nThe VetEndpointUtil should convert Vet entities to VetDto:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.api;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.api.SpecialtyListDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@Component\npublic class VetEndpointUtil {\n\n    public VetDto dtoFactory(Vet vet) {\n        VetDto dto = new VetDto();\n        dto.setId(vet.getId());\n        dto.setUuid(vet.getUuid());\n        dto.setFirstName(vet.getFirstName());\n        dto.setLastName(vet.getLastName());\n        List<SpecialtyDto> specialtyDtos = new ArrayList<>();\n        if (vet.getSpecialties() != null) {\n            for (Specialty s : vet.getSpecialties()) {\n                SpecialtyDto sdto = new SpecialtyDto();\n                sdto.setId(s.getId());\n                sdto.setUuid(s.getUuid());\n                sdto.setName(s.getName());\n                specialtyDtos.add(sdto);\n            }\n        }\n        SpecialtyListDto specialtyListDto = new SpecialtyListDto();\n        specialtyListDto.setSpecialties(specialtyDtos);\n        dto.setSpecialtyList(specialtyListDto);\n        return dto;\n    }\n\n    public VetListDto dtoListFactory(List<Vet> vets) {\n        List<VetDto> dtoList = new ArrayList<>();\n        for (Vet vet : vets) {\n            dtoList.add(dtoFactory(vet));\n        }\n        VetListDto listDto = new VetListDto();\n        listDto.setVets(dtoList);\n        return listDto;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 16. VisitDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 17. VisitListDto.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java\nWrite updated.\n\n### 18. VisitEndpointUtil.java\nRead: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java\nWrite updated.\n\nIMPORTANT RULES for DTOs:\n- Remove ALL jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.* imports\n- Remove ALL jakarta.json.bind.annotation.* imports  \n- Replace @JsonbProperty(\"fieldName\") with @JsonProperty(\"fieldName\") from com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation\n- Replace @JsonbDateFormat(\"yyyy-MM-dd\") with @JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\") from com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation\n- Add @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL) to DTOs if appropriate\n- Keep all Lombok annotations (@Getter, @Setter, @ToString, @EqualsAndHashCode, @NoArgsConstructor, @AllArgsConstructor)\n- For list DTOs, make sure they have a default constructor and proper getter/setter\n\nIMPORTANT RULES for EndpointUtil:\n- Replace @Stateless with @Component (from org.springframework.stereotype)\n- Remove @EJB, use @Autowired if needed\n- Remove dtoJsonFactory() and dtoXmlFactory() methods (Spring handles serialization)\n- Keep dtoFactory() and dtoListFactory() methods\n- Look at the actual entity-to-DTO mapping logic and preserve it\n- If EndpointUtil references other EndpointUtil classes (e.g., OwnerEndpointUtil uses PetEndpointUtil), inject them via @Autowired constructor\n\nFor each file, you MUST use the Read tool to read the file FIRST, and ONLY THEN use the Write tool. Use absolute paths starting with /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HzFHo4sYnJQJd6GigFokiD","session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"aa996e70-e67f-4bf1-a53f-f61b60069faf"}
