{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JHaq3oYbBWMcLsutvsU8rn","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully created all six Spring Data JPA repository interfaces to replace the Jakarta EE DAO pattern. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n## Created Repository Files\n\n### 1. **OwnerRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all owners ordered by name\n- Search owners by searchindex field\n\n### 2. **PetRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all pets ordered by name\n- Find pets by owner\n\n### 3. **PetTypeRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all pet types ordered by name\n- Find pet type by name\n- Search pet types by searchindex field\n\n### 4. **SpecialtyRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all specialties ordered by name\n- Find specialty by name\n- Search specialties by searchindex field\n\n### 5. **VetRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all vets ordered by name\n- Search vets by searchindex field\n\n### 6. **VisitRepository.java**\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitRepository.java`\n\nProvides methods to:\n- Find all visits ordered by date (descending)\n- Find visits by pet\n\n## Key Features\n\nAll repositories:\n- Extend `JpaRepository<Entity, Long>` for standard CRUD operations\n- Are annotated with `@Repository` for Spring component scanning\n- Use `@Query` annotations for custom JPQL queries\n- Use `@Param` annotations for named parameters\n- Leverage Spring Data JPA's query derivation for simple queries like `findByName`\n\nThese interfaces replace the old Jakarta EE DAO pattern with Spring Data JPA's more concise and powerful repository abstraction, eliminating the need for explicit DAO implementations."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"4b4fd6c5-f43d-4350-9cfa-f063b490847c"}
