{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HzFHo4sYnJQJd6GigFokiD","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all 18 Jakarta EE DTO and EndpointUtil classes to Spring Boot. Let me provide a comprehensive summary of the migration work completed.\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all Jakarta EE DTO and EndpointUtil classes to Spring Boot. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes made:\n\n### Files Migrated (18 total):\n\n#### Owner Domain (3 files):\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java**\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java**\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java**\n\n#### Pet Domain (3 files):\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java**\n5. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java**\n6. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java**\n\n#### PetType Domain (3 files):\n7. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java**\n8. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java**\n9. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java**\n\n#### Specialty Domain (3 files):\n10. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java**\n11. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java**\n12. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java**\n\n#### Vet Domain (3 files):\n13. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java**\n14. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java**\n15. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java**\n\n#### Visit Domain (3 files):\n16. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java**\n17. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java**\n18. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java**\n\n### Key Changes Applied:\n\n#### For DTOs (OwnerDto, PetDto, PetTypeDto, SpecialtyDto, VetDto, VisitDto and all List DTOs):\n\n**Removed:**\n- `@XmlRootElement`, `@XmlElement`, `@XmlAttribute`, `@XmlAccessorType` (JAXB annotations)\n- `@JsonbProperty`, `@JsonbDateFormat` (JSON-B annotations)\n- `implements Serializable` and `serialVersionUID`\n- All `jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*` imports\n- All `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.*` imports\n\n**Added:**\n- `@JsonProperty` from `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation` (replaced `@JsonbProperty`)\n- `@JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` from `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation` (replaced `@JsonbDateFormat`)\n\n**Kept:**\n- All Lombok annotations (`@Getter`, `@Setter`, `@ToString`, `@EqualsAndHashCode`, `@NoArgsConstructor`, `@AllArgsConstructor`)\n- All validation annotations (`@NotNull`, `@NotBlank`, `@NotEmpty`, `@Pattern`, `@Digits`)\n- All fields and their types\n\n#### For EndpointUtil Classes (OwnerEndpointUtil, PetEndpointUtil, PetTypeEndpointUtil, SpecialtyEndpointUtil, VetEndpointUtil, VisitEndpointUtil):\n\n**Removed:**\n- `@Stateless` annotation (Jakarta EE EJB)\n- `@EJB` injection annotations\n- `implements Serializable` and `serialVersionUID`\n- `dtoJsonFactory()` and `dtoListJsonFactory()` methods (JSON serialization)\n- `dtoXmlFactory()` and `dtoListXmlFactory()` methods (XML serialization)\n- All JAXB and JSON-B related imports\n\n**Added:**\n- `@Component` annotation from `org.springframework.stereotype`\n- `@Autowired` constructor injection for dependencies\n- Constructor-based dependency injection pattern\n\n**Kept:**\n- `dtoFactory()` methods (entity-to-DTO conversion logic)\n- `dtoListFactory()` methods (list conversion logic)\n- All business logic for converting entities to DTOs\n- `@Log` annotation for logging\n\n### Example of Migration Pattern:\n\n**Before (Jakarta EE):**\n```java\n@Stateless\npublic class OwnerEndpointUtil implements Serializable {\n    @EJB\n    private PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil;\n    \n    public String dtoJsonFactory(OwnerDto dto) throws JsonbException {\n        Jsonb jsonb = JsonbBuilder.create();\n        return jsonb.toJson(dto);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**After (Spring Boot):**\n```java\n@Component\npublic class OwnerEndpointUtil {\n    private final PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil;\n    \n    @Autowired\n    public OwnerEndpointUtil(PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil) {\n        this.petEndpointUtil = petEndpointUtil;\n    }\n    // No serialization methods - Spring handles this automatically\n}\n```\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot, with proper Jackson annotations for JSON serialization and Spring's component model for dependency injection."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"7634a294-09cf-4f17-b961-98ed142af9f5"}
