{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01V1HuuqPYuEbPGF8ytGhGb6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01GhpQwwTQ7qx8zHSd8y7oX8","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix entities and service interfaces","prompt":"CRITICAL FIX: The entity classes and service interfaces in the Spring Boot migration still reference deleted base classes. You need to fix ALL of these files.\n\nThe project is at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nThe following classes have been DELETED and can no longer be referenced:\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.EntityBase\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.EntityBaseObject\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.CrudDao\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.CrudService\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.SearchableService\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.SearchableEntity\n- org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.db.EntityListenerLogger\n- All *Listener.java files (OwnerListener, PetListener, etc.)\n\n## Entity files to fix:\nFor each entity, READ the file first, then WRITE the fixed version.\n\n### Owner.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java\nChanges needed:\n- Remove `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.EntityBaseObject;`\n- Remove `extends EntityBaseObject` from class declaration\n- Remove `@EntityListeners(OwnerListener.class)` if present\n- Keep all JPA annotations, validation annotations, Lombok annotations\n- The class should just implement `Comparable<Owner>, Serializable`\n\n### Pet.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java\nChanges needed:\n- Remove `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.EntityBase;`\n- Remove `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.EntityBaseObject;`\n- Remove `extends EntityBaseObject`\n- Remove `implements EntityBase` \n- Remove `@EntityListeners(PetListener.class)` if present\n- Keep `implements Comparable<Pet>, Serializable`\n\n### PetType.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java\nSame approach as Pet.java\n\n### Specialty.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java\nSame approach\n\n### Vet.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java\nSame approach\n\n### Visit.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java\nSame approach\n\n## Service interface files to fix:\n\n### OwnerService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerService.java\nIt currently extends CrudService and SearchableService. Remove those extends and just define the methods directly:\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface OwnerService {\n    List<Owner> getAll();\n    Owner findById(long id);\n    Owner addNew(Owner owner);\n    Owner update(Owner owner);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Owner> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit);\n    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner);\n    String getPetsAsString(Owner owner);\n}\n```\n\n### PetService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetService.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface PetService {\n    Pet addNew(Pet pet);\n    List<Pet> getAll();\n    Pet findById(long petId);\n    Pet update(Pet pet);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Visit> getVisits(Pet pet);\n    List<Pet> getAllPetsOfAnOwner(Owner entity);\n}\n```\n\n### PetTypeService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeService.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface PetTypeService {\n    List<PetType> getAll();\n    void delete(long id);\n    PetType addNew(PetType petType);\n    PetType findById(long id);\n    PetType update(PetType petType);\n    List<PetType> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    PetType findByName(String name);\n}\n```\n\n### SpecialtyService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyService.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface SpecialtyService {\n    List<Specialty> getAll();\n    Specialty findById(long id);\n    Specialty addNew(Specialty specialty);\n    Specialty update(Specialty specialty);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Specialty> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n    Specialty findSpecialtyByName(String name);\n}\n```\n\n### VetService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetService.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface VetService {\n    List<Vet> getAll();\n    Vet findById(long id);\n    void delete(long id);\n    Vet addNew(Vet vet);\n    Vet update(Vet vet);\n    List<Vet> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n}\n```\n\n### VisitService.java\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitService.java\n```java\npackage 