{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01TVQg2q99jBYJY2wzwxWMgC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration complete. Here's the final summary:\n\n## Migration Results\n\n**Jakarta EE 10 -> Spring Boot 3.2.5** - All tasks completed successfully.\n\n### What was done:\n1. **Build system**: Complete pom.xml rewrite (WAR -> JAR, Jakarta EE deps -> Spring Boot starters)\n2. **Configuration**: New `PetclinicApplication.java`, `application.properties`, `data.sql`\n3. **6 Entity classes**: Removed EE base classes, kept JPA/validation annotations\n4. **6 Spring Data JPA repositories**: Replaced DAO+EntityManager pattern\n5. **12 Service files**: EJB `@Stateless` -> Spring `@Service` with constructor injection\n6. **6 REST controllers**: JAX-RS `@Path/@GET` -> Spring MVC `@RestController/@GetMapping`\n7. **12 DTO files**: JAXB/JSON-B -> Jackson annotations\n8. **6 EndpointUtil files**: `@Stateless` -> `@Component`\n9. **Dockerfile**: Updated CMD to `java -jar`\n10. **Smoke tests**: 28 pytest tests\n\n### Errors resolved:\n- Old Arquillian tests removed (incompatible with Spring Boot)\n- Entity/service base class references fixed after deletion\n- `data.sql` column name `lastname` corrected to `last_name` (Spring Boot's `SpringPhysicalNamingStrategy` transforms camelCase `@Column` names)\n- Smoke tests updated to handle plain JSON array responses\n\n### Final test results: **28/28 passed**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":686,"cache_read_input_tokens":62599,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":686,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":379},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3e9f2b3-1305-43ae-9feb-99d287ff0491","uuid":"e83a21a7-51af-46f2-8dbf-f19839229f45"}
